sources.title: Bonanza (TV-1960) THE BLOOD LINE (S1E22)
sources.description:
This Timeless TV Western starring Lorne Green, Pernell Roberts, Dan Blocker and Michael Landon, is one of the most popular shows in television history!

THE BLOOD LINE: The son of Luke Grayson arrives from the East and learns that Ben Cartwright shot and killed his father. Ben fired only in self-defense and feels badly for young young man. Todd Grayson vows revenge and recruits a professional gunman to get back at the Cartwrights.
